quran[10]{c,v,t,f}:
  38,17,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Ihanganire ivyo bavuga bikubangamiye, uheze wibuke n’Umuja wacu Dawudi yaranzwe n’inguvu zo guhangana n’abansi ata guhesha, hamwe rero no kwihanganira igamburukiramana. Mu vy’ukuri, yarigaya cane akitura kenshi Imana Allah<sup>2</sup>.","[2] Iyi Aayah iratera intege Intumwa Muhamadi (nyakugira amahoro n’impuhwe z’Imana Allah)."
  38,18,"Mu vy’ukuri Twebwe Allah, Twatumye imisozi yitabira itazira n’ininahazamana ryagirwa na Dawudi umugoroba n’igitondo;",""
  38,19,"Dutuma n’umugwi w’inyoni witabira nya tazira n’ininahazamana, ivyo vyose rero vyaramwumvira;",""
  38,20,"Twaranamutsimbatarije ubwami bwiwe kw’ijunja n’inguvu Twamuhaye, Tumuha n’ubutumwa hamwe no gutomora ijambo n’ingingo.",""
  38,21,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Mbega warashikiriwe n’inkuru y’abantu babiri batase, igihe basimba urugo rw’aho Dawudi yasengera;",""
  38,22,"Baraheza bamwinjirirako aca agira ubwoba! Ni ho bamutururuza bati: “Tekana, ntugire ubwoba namba, twebwe twatase, aho umwe muri twebwe yarenganije uwundi; twaje kukwitura rero kugira udutunganirize vy’ukuri ata nkunzi, wongere uduhanure gukurikira inzira igororotseˮ.",""
  38,23,"Ni ho rero umwe muri bo yatangura kwigana avuga ati: “Mu vy’ukuri, uyu ni mwenewacu, afise intama mirongo icenda n’icenda, nanje nkaba mfise intama imwe rudende, akaba yagize inambu yo kuyinyaga, aca ambwira ati: “Mpa iyo ntamaˮ, maze aranzivya sinagira ayo ncira n’ayo miraˮ;",""
  38,24,"Dawudi aca avuga ati: “Ni ukuri, mwenewanyu yakurenganije mu kukunyaga intama yawe akayihagira, kandi abenshi mu basangiye amatungo, ni ukuri birashika bamwe muri bo bakarenganya abandi, havuyemwo gusa abemeramana bakora ivyiza bitegetswe, ntibarenganyana. Abo rero, ni bake cane mu bantuˮ. Dawudi yaratahuye ko Twebwe Allah, Twamugerageje mu kuba abo bantu baje kumwitwarako, ni ho yasaba imbabazi Imana yiwe Rurema Allah, aca arayubamira ashira uruhanga hasi, maze arigaya<sup>3</sup>;","[3] Iyo umuntu asomye iyi Aayah gushika ku mpera, aca yubama agashira uruhanga hasi."
  38,25,"Twaciye Tumugumiriza akabanga Turanamubabarira ivyaha vyiwe. Mu vy’ukuri Dawudi, ni ukuri ari mu batonye kuri Twebwe Allah, ari no mu bagenewe uburuhukiro bwiza mu buzima bw’inyuma yo gupfa.",""
  38,26,"Ni ho rero Twamubwira Duti: “Ewe Dawudi! Mu vy’ukuri, Tukugize icariho cacu mu kukugira umwami kw’isi. Kubera ivyo rero, tunganiriza abantu vy’ukuri ata nkunzi, kandi ntugakurikire ivyipfuzo vyawe mu gufata ingingo, kuko vyoguhubisha inzira y’amabwirizwa y’idini ry’Imana Allah. Mu vy’ukuri abahuba inzira y’amabwirizwa y’idini ry’Imana Allah, barategekanirijwe ibihano bikaze, kuko birengagije umusi w’iharurirwa ry’ibiremwa<sup>4</sup>ˮ.","[4] Iyi Aayah ihanura indongozi ko zibwirizwa gutunganiriza abantu vy’ukuri ata nkunzi, kuko kutabatunganiriza kuzihubisha inzira y’amabwirizwa y’idini ry’Imana Allah."
